name: Leave None Behind (Canceled)
blurb: Take control of three captives. Your task is to find a way out, overcome puzzling obstacles, and discover why you are there.

rewards.reward:
LABORER
============================== 
NEWSLETTER
============================== 
You get our personal thank you. Everything helps. Seriously. You've helped get this game on its feet. Thank you! This will also give you access to our exclusive newsletter for Kickstarter backers only.

●● ~US$0.90

APPRENTICE
============================== 
WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
Spruce up your desktop/smartphone/tablet with a package of beautiful HD Leave None Behind concept art, created by one of our talented artists.

●● ~US$4.50

[EARLY BIRD] TRADESMAN
============================== 
GAME + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
You've managed to stay ahead of the pack and score yourself a copy of the game! Kudos! You get a digital download of Leave None Behind when it is released.

●● ~US$9.00

TRADESMAN
============================== 
GAME + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
You get a digital download of Leave None Behind when it is released.

GAME + GIFT + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
Receive a digital download of Leave None Behind when it is released, along with another copy to share with friends.

CURATOR
============================== 
DIGITAL ARTBOOK + GAME + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
Art enthusiast? When the game is released, you will receive a PDF of all the artwork featured in Leave None Behind. This includes concept art, early sketches of characters, environments, and technology, and goes through the entire planning process of the Leave None Behind artists.

●● ~US$26.90

CONDUCTOR
============================== 
DIGITAL SOUNDTRACK + GAME + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
Music enthusiast? When the game is released, you will receive a digital soundtrack of over fifty tracks featured in Leave None Behind, as well as exclusive hidden tracks created during the development process that aren't featured in the game.

TECHNICIAN
============================== 
DIGITAL ARTBOOK + DIGITAL SOUNDTRACK
GAME + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
Can't decide? When the game is released, you will receive both a digital copy of the soundtrack, and a PDF of all artwork featured in Leave None Behind!

The Soundtrack includes over fifty tracks featured in Leave None Behind, as well as exclusive hidden tracks created during the development process that aren't featured in the game.

The Artbook includes concept art, early sketches of characters, environments, and technology, and goes through the entire planning process of the Leave None Behind artists.

●● ~US$35.90

ARTISAN
============================== 
ILLUSTRATED PRINTS + DIGITAL ARTBOOK + DIGITAL SOUNDTRACK + GAME + WALLPAPER PACK

BETA ACCESS + ILLUSTRATED PRINTS + DIGITAL ARTBOOK + DIGITAL SOUNDTRACK + GAME + WALLPAPER PACK
============================== 
Receive the Artisan package and get access to the Leave None Behind closed beta! Play the game months before release, and help shape the game by giving your opinions, criticisms, and bug reports.

PROSPECTOR
============================== 
WILHELM'S PROSPECTUS + 
ACKNOWLEDGEMENT IN CREDITS

- Wilhelm's Journal [Physical artbook and novel]
- Illustrated Prints [Signed on request]

OVERSEER

EXECUTIVE

Receive everything explained above, and have a chat with Deniz Celtek, our Art Director, and discuss an asset of the game you would like to help create. It can be a machine, a boss, or anything you can think of!

Flights and accommodation not included.
